theorem Topology.closure_interior_union {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior (A ∪ B : Set X)) = closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  have h : interior (A ∪ B : Set X) = interior A ∪ interior B := by
    simpa using interior_union
  calc
    closure (interior (A ∪ B : Set X))
        = closure (interior A ∪ interior B) := by
          simpa [h]
    _ = closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
          simpa using closure_union

theorem Topology.closed_P3_implies_P1 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hClosed : IsClosed A) (hP3 : Topology.P3 (X := X) A) :
    Topology.P1 (X := X) A := by
  have hOpen : IsOpen A :=
    Topology.closed_P3_isOpen (X := X) (A := A) hClosed hP3
  exact Topology.isOpen_implies_P1 (X := X) (A := A) hOpen
